                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>U. S. Circuit Clerks Office</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"align(right)\"><placeName>St Paul</placeName>, <date>Nov. 20. 1862</date></p>\n            <p><addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee>.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">My dear Sir.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">The package containing<lb/> the books and letters arrived here on the<lb/>\n                <date>18<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi></date> inst, and therein enclose the amount<lb/> of\n                your bill &amp; 5.53. which I trust will<lb/> come safe to hand.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I have delayed till to day to forward<lb/> this in hopes to be able\n                to send you a<lb/> list of subscribers for the Occident, and<lb/> also to order some\n                copies of the Bible<lb/> but I have not had time to give the<lb/> matter much\n                attention. I have sold<lb/> 1 copy of the Bible, and have no doubt<lb/> if I had\n                them here could dispose<lb/> of ½ a dozen at least, and obtain<lb/> the cash on\n                delivery and would remit<lb/> it at once. I also trust in my next<lb/> communication\n                which I will write</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p37s7jc5q/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
