                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>in about a week from this to send<lb/> you a list of half dozen subscribers<lb/> for\n                the Occident in their city! All tho<lb/> Israelites here are Germans and can<lb/>\n                read but little English and therefore<lb/> I do not suppose that much could be<lb/>\n                done in the sale of <persName>Dias'</persName> letters, tho' I<lb/> shall endeavor\n                to dispose of the two<lb/> copies sent and if more are required<lb/> will inform\n                you.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I understand that you have a<lb/> much smaller and cheaper\n                edition<lb/> of the bible—if so, I could dispose<lb/> of some for you; at this\n                season of<lb/> the year the expense of sending a<lb/> package here is more than it\n                would<lb/> be in the summer time when the<lb/> river is open for navigation. Do\n                you<lb/> count the expense of transmitting<lb/> the books <add>?</add>? I will\n                willingly<lb/> do all I can to dispose of any of<lb/> your publications, and you\n                can<lb/> send them if you think best at</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p37s7jc5q/canvas/p2"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
